  "title": "Senior Sales Manager – Pipeline & Steel Products [EL]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Scope of Role</strong></p><ul><li><p>Develop new business while maintaining and strengthening key client relationships.</p></li><li><p>Identify growth opportunities across markets, products, and service offerings.</p></li><li><p>Partner with internal teams to deliver customized solutions to clients.</p></li><li><p>Lead proposal development, contract negotiations, and sales closures.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Profile</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in Business, Engineering, or a related field.</p></li><li><p>At least 5 years of industry experience within oilfield services or oil & gas equipment sales.</p></li><li><p>In-depth knowledge of drilling, completion, and production-related products.</p></li><li><p>Strong communication, presentation, and stakeholder management skills.</p></li><li><p>Proactive, target-driven, and flexible to travel.</p></li></ul><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
